ygData.messageBody:
Okay so I have heard that<br> there were plenty
of<br> beautiful Voluptuous<br> Michigan
Ladies,Gothic<br> and bbws everquest<br> gamers of many
different<br> ages,races and<br> nationalities and all<br>
shapes and sizes out<br> there but I haven't seen<br>
any. So I set this club up<br> to find out.This club
is for<br> those from the<br>
Midland/Saginaw/Sanford<br> and other places in<br> Michigan! If any of
you<br> ladies are out there post a<br> message and a
picture<br> and Come on in, sit a<br> spell, throw your
fingers in<br> motion to introduce<br> yourself.Kind of
open here,<br> Check out what others<br> have said and
maybe<br> you'll have some input as<br> well. everquest
dating<br> service is a great club to<br> be a member of -
that is, if<br> you contribute to it and<br> not be
shy. Only you &<br> other Michiganders alike<br> can
make it a place worth<br> stopping in and dropping
a<br> few lines and only thing is<br> this club does
not accept<br> swingers/mate swappings<br> or any
other alternative<br> lifestyle choice that some<br>
make and so if your into<br> any of those then
please<br> step away from the
club!<br><a href=http://clubs.yahoo.com/clubs/everquestdatingservice target=new>http://clubs.yahoo.com/clubs/everquestdatingservice</a>
